---
title: Quick Creamy Pulled Beef Ragu & Linguine with Garlic Pangrattato & Mixed Salad
description: This sumptuous yet simple pasta is absolute decadence, from the rich pulled beef ragu infused with Nan's special seasoning, to
the crunch from the garlic pangrattato. Don’t be too surprised if the bowls are left licked clean!

*Keep an eye out... Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be slightly different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
